 class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104crd1665703135753.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/crd1665703135753.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/crd1665703135753.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"crd1665703135753\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"crd1665703135753__updelocc_406863\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Remove an occurrence of the specified entity from the hitlist.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"crd1665703135753__topic_d122798e1_d122799e1_d122800e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104crd1665703135753_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"crd1665703135753__codeblock_ghw_232_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long updelocc (unsigned char*Entity, longOccnum);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crd1665703135753__topic_d86897e1_d86898e1_d86899e1_d86900e1_d86901e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1199570e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"crd1665703135753__parml_tns_g32_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the entity. You can specify zero or an empty string to denote the current\n                  entity</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Occnum</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Sequence number of the occurrence to be deleted. Specify -1 to remove the last\n                  occurrence in the hitlist, or zero to remove the current occurrence.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crd1665703135753__topic_d86902e1_d86903e1_d86904e1_d86905e1_d86906e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1199570e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"crd1665703135753__table_d14945e1_d14946e1_d14947e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by updelocc</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"crd1665703135753__table_d14945e1_d14946e1_d14947e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"crd1665703135753__table_d14945e1_d14946e1_d14947e1__entry__2\">Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"crd1665703135753__table_d14945e1_d14946e1_d14947e1__entry__1\">\n &gt;0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"crd1665703135753__table_d14945e1_d14946e1_d14947e1__entry__2\">The sequence number of the occurrence that\n                        became current after removing. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"crd1665703135753__table_d14945e1_d14946e1_d14947e1__entry__1\">\n -1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"crd1665703135753__table_d14945e1_d14946e1_d14947e1__entry__2\">The occurrence could not be removed. Most\n                        likely causes: <var class=\"keyword varname\">Occnum</var> is out of range, or\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> does not exist, or it is not painted on the\n                        component. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crd1665703135753__topic_d86907e1_d86908e1_d86909e1_d86910e1_d86911e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1199570e148\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crd1665703135753__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"crd1665703135753__topic_d86912e1_d86913e1_d86914e1_d86915e1_d86916e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1199570e161\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crd1665703135753__p_d122819e1_d122820e1_d122821e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">updelocc</code> removes the occurrence of\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">entity</var> having the sequence number <var class=\"keyword varname\">Occnum</var>. If\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is zero or an empty string, the current entity is used.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"crd1665703135753__note_N100DE_N100C2_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">updelocc</code> returns 1 even when the last occurrence was removed, so you\n            cannot use <code class=\"ph codeph\">updelocc</code> in a loop to remove all occurrences.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"crd1665703135753__p_d122822e1_d122823e1_d122824e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">updelocc</code> is equivalent to the\n            ProcScript <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">remocc</span> statement, where you can find more information\n            about the rules for removing occurrences.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104crd1665703135753_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"crd1665703135753__codeblock_u4j_432_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nEXPORT void DELOCC ()\n{\nupdelocc(0, 0); /* Revove current occurrence of current entity */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryi1665703135669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>upaddocc</a><p>Create an empty occurrence of an entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qem1665703135824.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>updisocc</a><p>Discard one or more occurrences of the specified entity from the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hor1665703135893.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>upsetocc</a><p>Make the specified occurrence current.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526582\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526582\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "updelocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Remove an occurrence of the specified entity from the hitlist. Explain this code long updelocc (unsigned char*Entity, longOccnum); Copy Parameters Entity Name of the entity. You can specify zero or an empty string to denote the current entity Occnum Sequence number of the occurrence to be deleted. Specify -1 to remove the last occurrence in the hitlist, or zero to remove the current occurrence. Return Values Table 1. Values returned by updelocc Value Meaning >0 The sequence number of the occurrence that became current after removing. -1 The occurrence could not be removed. Most likely causes: Occnum is out of range, or Entity does not exist, or it is not painted on the component. Use Library: yrtl Description updelocc removes the occurrence of entity having the sequence number Occnum . If Entity is zero or an empty string, the current entity is used. Note: updelocc returns 1 even when the last occurrence was removed, so you cannot use updelocc in a loop to remove all occurrences. updelocc is equivalent to the ProcScript remocc statement, where you can find more information about the rules for removing occurrences. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void DELOCC () { updelocc(0, 0); /* Revove current occurrence of current entity */ } Copy Related Links upaddocc Create an empty occurrence of an entity. updisocc Discard one or more occurrences of the specified entity from the hitlist. upsetocc Make the specified occurrence current. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}